  <brief_title>Randomized Trial of Home Versus Clinic-based Screening for Sexually Transmitted Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Trial of Home Versus Clinic-based Screening for Sexually Transmitted Infections in Long-Acting Reversible Contraceptive Users</official_title>
