  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study randomizes women using long-acting reversible methods of contraception to
      home-based STD screening through the mail compared to screening available in a clinical
      setting. We hypothesize that women randomized to home-based screening will be more likely to
      complete screening.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
